From: "Bernhard R. Beck" <beckbr@touch.ch>

In the message Cholera, imported - New Zealand (02) posted
18.09.2001 the moderator mentioned that [mainland China has not
reported Cholera this year.
In the WHO Weekly Epidemiological Record 2001, vol.76 page 224
[mainland China reported 140 cholera cases in the period 30 May to 25
Jun 2001. <http://www.who.int/wer/pdf/2001/wer7629.pdf>
